# LL-013
# Title:     Integration tests for deprecated endpoints must be updated alongside unit tests
# Milestone: M9
# Source:    M9-S5 QUALITY GATE — test_m4_jobs_queues.py::TestQueuesContentionEndpointIntegration
# Lesson:    When ISS-018 was fixed (unit test_jobs.py updated for M7 per-class queue contention),
#            the corresponding integration tests in test_m4_jobs_queues.py were not updated.
#            This was caught during M9 full-suite run: 4 integration tests failed because they
#            still tested GET /queues/contention (old M4 aggregate shape) which returns 404.
#            Fix: Update both unit AND integration tests when an endpoint shape changes.
#            Pattern: grep for the old endpoint URL across ALL test files before closing a milestone.
# Apply to:  M9 and all future milestones that change or remove an API endpoint.
